{
  "stem": "16442.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 436.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The last transport was coming, if I remember good, from Lodz, from the Lodz Ghetto, which was towards the fall.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then the transports stopped.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So our work was finished.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then I was transferred to a place called the Weberei, where we used to do these [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] things.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They brought us some leather strips.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We used to make ribbons out of them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And all sorts of things we were working there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Maybe that was about the last month or so, the last six weeks.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The very last few weeks in Auschwitz-Birkenau was no more work, no more food.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We were just laying in our barracks doing nothing, getting almost no food, and sitting and waiting.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Were a few selections.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we were always less and less because some of them went to the-- to the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We're left.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Until New Year's Eve, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] a couple of SS came in to the barracks where we were and called out my number, 6684.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I was with a few girls together.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they begged me not to go because I was the only one to call.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "You know, you stick together.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "A few girls-- in your sorrows, you stick together.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I was the only one called then.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I told the girls, I believe in destiny.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Whatever has to happen to me-- if they'll take me to the gas chamber, that's where I'm going.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They called my number.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I'm going.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I left them there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "That was the day-- the night when they took us, undressed us, took everything away from us, and they gave us one piece of so-called dress-- a summer dress, the 1st of January-- and put us into wagons.",
      "word_count": 38
    }
  ],
